      "date": "2012-08-15 22:43:49.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/1afc4266-e725-11e1-ac43-52540035b04c).  Ran 33 tests.  4 tests failed: performance-sanity, mmp, replay-single, lfsck.",
